      1          /**
      2           *  @file       HeaterLoad.c
      3           *
      4           *  @brief      Load Handler that performs delayed activation between two pins required to activate load
      5           *
      6           *  @details    This module executes heater activation with a predefined sequence:
      7           *              - If Pilot is DigitalOutputPilot or MultiDriver, it toggles Pin1, wait time, then toggles Pin2
      8           *              - If Pilot is MultiSequence, sequence has to be set in Pilot configuration;
      9           *                  it will use Sequence 1 to OFF, Sequence 2 to ON
     10           *              - Any other Pilot type will not perform any sequence at all
     11           *              Wait time can be customized defining HBL_LOAD_HEATER_DELAY with value in ms; ; if undefined, default set is 100ms
     12           *
     13           *  @section    Applicable_Documents
     14           *					List here all the applicable documents if needed. <tr>	
     15           *
     16           *  $Header: $
     17           *
     18           *  @copyright  Copyright 2017-$Date$. Whirlpool Corporation. All rights reserved - CONFIDENTIAL
     19           */
